<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to YourApp Creator Program!</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .logo { max-width: 150px; }
    h1 { color: #4a4a4a; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #e74c3c; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; }
    .benefits { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { margin-top: 40px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <img src="{{appUrl}}/images/creator-logo.png" alt="YourApp Creator Program" class="logo">
  </div>

  <h1>Welcome to the Creator Program, {{firstName}}!</h1>
  
  <p>Congratulations on joining our exclusive Creator Program! We're thrilled to have you as part of our creative community.</p>
  
  <p>As a creator on YourApp, you'll have access to special tools and opportunities to grow your audience and maximize your impact.</p>
  
  <div class="benefits">
    <h3>Your Creator Benefits Include:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Analytics dashboard with audience insights</li>
      <li>Priority content placement</li>
      <li>Monetization opportunities</li>
      <li>Early access to new features</li>
      <li>Creator support team</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  
  <p>To get started, visit your Creator Dashboard where you can manage your content, track performance, and access creator tools.</p>
  
  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Go to Creator Dashboard</a>
  </div>
  
  <p>Want to see how your content is performing? Check out your <a href="{{analyticsUrl}}">Analytics</a> to track engagement and growth.</p>
  
  <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, your dedicated creator support team is ready to help. Just reply to this email!</p>
  
  <p>Looking forward to seeing your amazing content,<br>The YourApp Creator Team</p>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© {{currentYear}} YourApp. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>123 App Street, San Francisco, CA 94107</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>